data.name: GT_NCFWarnText.Text
data.value: The controls on this page have been disabled because you have chosen experimentally supported game which settings are stored in the cloud. You can load graphics settings file in a text editor to manually edit. Changes made in this file take effect the next time you start the game. Be extremely careful.

data.name: GT_NCF_LoadNotepad.Text
data.value: Load settings file in a text editor

data.name: FP_TopLabel.Text
data.value: On this page you can install one of available and tested by us FPS-configs into the game. FPS-config is a file autoexec.cfg, which can significantly increase the performance of the game with loss of a picture quality. You can edit installed FPS-config manually later in Config Editor tab. Attention! If you use FPS-config the Graphic Tweaker will not be able to edit graphic settings (the settings obtained from the config have higher priority).

data.value: Show BackUp file in Windows Explorer
